\
The topology can be reshaped by a small set of canonical operators.  \
Each is:\
- **Idempotent** under its guard conditions (calling twice has no further effect).\
- **Composable** (multiple can fire in a single tick; stackable inside the Sigil Ring).\
- **Bounded** by motion/energy budgets (no free moves, no unbounded growth).\
\
---\
