- **Sigil House**: Weaving.\
\
### **Prune(E,\uc0\u954 )**\
- **Action**: attenuate or remove edge(s) in set E.  \
- **Guard**: coherence low (edge weight disagrees with geometry), volatility > \uc0\u954 , reliability low.  \
- **Effect**: reduce weight, possibly delete edge; free nutrients routed back.  \
- **Sigil House**: Purification.\
\
### **Fuse(C1,C2)**\
- **Action**: merge clusters C1, C2 into single cluster.  \
- **Guard**: sustained co-firing across ticks, low tension between, strong nutrient/energy overlap.  \
- **Effect**: new node/cluster with combined energy/health; edges merged; IDs mapped.  \
- **Sigil House**: Memory/Weaving (fusion as rebirth).\
\
### **Fission(C,\uc0\u968 )**\
- **Action**: split brittle or entropic cluster C into two.  \
- **Guard**: internal entropy high, coherence low, multiple tension ridges inside cluster.  \
- **Effect**: partition nodes; redistribute edges; \uc0\u968  controls split bias.  \
- **Sigil House**: Purification/Flame (controlled burn).\
\
