- **Effect**: N.layer \uc0\u8592  max(0, N.layer\u8722 1); rebloom path triggered if surface reached.  \
- **Sigil House**: Memory (resurrection).\
\
### **Sink(N\uc0\u8594 Layer\u8595 )**\
